{"tid":2424292,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鋼琴女神扮電玩美女還原度超高！酥胸蜜桃臀「微笑線」辣爆","createTime":"2021-02-26T12:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T05:13:31.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9e8e4b98b038e46bf60a0cb0120fe4ab10267c","tid":2424292,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:46:02.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞「鋼琴女神」李元玲（Cathryn Li）靠著高超琴技、姣好臉蛋擄獲不少粉絲的心，平時愛曬出惹火辣照撫慰一眾宅男粉絲。為追求新鮮感，近日她大玩角色扮演（Cosplay），包括扮演電玩《太空戰士Ⅶ》（Final Fantasy Ⅶ）中的女主角「蒂法」，又換上和服化身櫻花妹。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/08/2762631-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F08%2F2762631-PH.jpg&h=7a545602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「鋼琴女神」李元玲面容姣好身材惹火，令女粉絲相當欽羨。（圖／翻攝自李元玲IG）<br />\n<br />\n日前她才秀出4張超搶眼比基尼照，上下全露讓粉絲鼻血狂噴。只見李元玲身穿黃色比基尼，中間辣開U型洞的剪裁設計，讓飽滿雙峰險些遮不住，往下一看，私密地帶更是惹火，胯下雪白肌膚幾乎全被看光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/26/3042805-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F26%2F3042805-PH.jpg&h=ee2f0233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼李元玲角色扮演《太空戰士Ⅶ》女主角之一的「蒂法」。（圖／翻攝自李元玲IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/26/3042803-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F26%2F3042803-PH.jpg&h=069ac870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這次更是繼先前萬聖節扮演「神力女超人」後，再度Cosplay讓人相當驚艷，火辣的「蒂法」前胸擋不住「峰」情，轉到背面，超短黑色皮裙讓渾圓蜜桃臀「微笑線」兇猛入鏡，S曲線腰身同樣一覽無遺，加上帥氣神情簡直神還原電玩造型，令人相當驚艷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/26/3042806-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F26%2F3042806-PH.jpg&h=77cd6432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李元玲角色扮演背面超短皮裙直逼蜜桃臀。（圖／翻攝自李元玲IG）<br />\n<br />\n李元玲更問網友：「喜歡哪一個造型？」所有網友幾乎一面倒投選「蒂法」造型，更有網友讚她「比蒂法更吸引人！」、「線條超好看」、「超美的啦，只有女神才能展現這種辣！」"},{"pid":"57fa085c9e6c0037e258b5c57d7e9c28cfbbfea3","tid":2424292,"uid":271130,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"呢條女真係好煩 成日想上位<br />\n<br />\n乜野鋼牙女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5a07032174145dd6d674a1a5b4b7d0d7ec93c0","tid":2424292,"uid":308570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:51:58.000Z","msg":"屌打牙隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9864985d95256cead70284ce6cd31268e892c5f","tid":2424292,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b5a07032174145dd6d674a1a5b4b7d0d7ec93c0","tid":2424292,"uid":308570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:51:58.000Z","msg":"屌打牙隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"醜方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096e23a4a41f268f1ab21ae10c7ff3a80be90634","tid":2424292,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:55:10.000Z","msg":"佢真係好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔靚....."},{"pid":"a882cc9eb622d860feca7c99b0872d8d25d47a4a","tid":2424292,"uid":46966,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完係唔撚似喎屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394b96dc13d7e2f74ce2d0b290d5eef43e5a3d81","tid":2424292,"uid":85965,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"Cosplay tifa都係嘉倩正d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\